        "content": "<p>For a feature in mathlib4, I needed the following part of <code>applySimpResultToProp</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">applySimpResultToProp'</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">proof</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Expr</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">prop</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Expr</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">r</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">Simp.Result</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">MetaM</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">Expr</span> <span class=\"bp\">×</span> <span class=\"n\">Expr</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">do</span>\n  <span class=\"k\">match</span> <span class=\"n\">r.proof</span><span class=\"bp\">?</span> <span class=\"k\">with</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">some</span> <span class=\"n\">eqProof</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">return</span> <span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span> <span class=\"n\">mkEqMP</span> <span class=\"n\">eqProof</span> <span class=\"n\">proof</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">r.expr</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"bp\">|</span> <span class=\"n\">none</span> <span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"n\">r.expr</span> <span class=\"bp\">!=</span> <span class=\"n\">prop</span> <span class=\"k\">then</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">return</span> <span class=\"o\">((</span><span class=\"bp\">←</span> <span class=\"n\">mkExpectedTypeHint</span> <span class=\"n\">proof</span> <span class=\"n\">r.expr</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"n\">r.expr</span><span class=\"o\">)